items.longDescription: <ul><li>Part of the Super Mario Bros 30th Anniversary series.</li><li>About Mario - Mario's style has evolved throughout his many adventures and challenges. This blocky, classic look harkens back to his design in the original Super Mario Bros. game that launched for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1985. His iconic red overalls and brownish shirt represent the classic color scheme used in the original game.</li><li>Discover the Power Inside!</li><li>Your favorite Nintendo characters come to life in surprising ways in different games.</li><li>Tap amiibo figures to the Wii U GamePad controller to interact with compatible games, no portal needed.</li><li>Each compatible game offers different ways to interact with your amiibo figure. Depending on the game, they can grow and learn as they compete alongside you, give you access to specials items, or let you customize your characters and your gameplay.</li><li>Games with amiibo compatibility in 2014 include Super Smash Bros. for Wii U, Mario Kart 8 and Hyrule Warriors. Additional games with planned amiibo functionality include Mario Party 10, Kirby and the Rainbow Curse, Captain Toad: Treasure Tracker, Yoshi's Woolly World and more!</li><li>Visit amiibo.com to learn more about upcoming amiibo figures and compatible games! Compatibility and functionality may vary per game.</li><li>Compatibility with Nintendo 3DS coming in 2015.</li><li>amiibo in Super Smash Bros. for Wii U: Customize your amiibo figure as the ultimate sidekick, and level it up to CRUSH your opponents. Train your amiibo to supercharge its stats and expand its abilities. Customize your amiibo by adjusting its attack, defense and speed stats. Fight your amiibo against a friend's to make them tougher and see who the best trainer is. Team up with your amiibo, or battle against friends in multiplayer amiibo action.</li><li>amiibo in Mario Kart 8: Receive special racing suits for your Mii character based on each amiibo character's look. Dress up your Mii like fan-favorite characters such as Mario, Yoshi, Kirby or even Samus Aran. Compatible with the following amiibo figures: Mario, Luigi, Peach, Yoshi, Donkey Kong, Link, Captain Falcon, Kirby, Samus, Fox.</li><li>amiibo in Hyrule Warriors: Tap the Link amiibo figure to receive a new weapon to use in battle: the Spinner from The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess game. Tap the Zelda amiibo figure once per day to get a weapon rated 3 stars or higher. Tap any other amiibo figure once per day to get randomly selected materials, weapons or Rupees in the game.</li></ul>

items.name: Legend of Zelda Twilight Princess HD with Wolf Link / Midna amiibo (Wii U)
items.categoryPath: Video Games/Nintendo Wii U / Wii/Wii U Games
items.shortDescription: A dark force, shrouded in twilight, has invaded the vast land of Hyrule. To restore light to the world, team up with the mysterious creature Midna and embrace the darkness to transform into a divine wolf. Fight through labyrinthine dungeons, survive puzzling traps, and meet a cast of characters you'll never forget in this legendary Zelda adventure. You can also get an exclusive Wolf Link/Midna amiibo and add bonuses to this title and the upcoming Legend of Zelda game for Wii U, launching in 2016.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess HD is the best way to experience this critically acclaimed game.</li><li>Explore a vast Hyrule, a mysterious Twilight Realm, and masterfully-designed dungeons.</li><li>Restore balance to the world with the aid of the impish Midna and your divine wolf powers.</li><li>Transform into a divine wolf to solve puzzles with your 6th sense and battle creatures corrupted by the twilight.</li><li>Meet a cast of friendly folk and interesting characters, like the entrepreneurial baby Malo and even a yeti couple.</li><li>Nab the exclusive Wolf Link amiibo and carry data over to the upcoming Legend of Zelda game for Wii U, launching in 2016.</li><li>ESRB Rating: TEEN with Animated Blood and Fantasy Violence</li></ul>
